<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,340,1463,1488]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Seasonality.</emphasis>
January, February, April–October (
<bibRefCitation author="Boero" box="[742,974,1463,1488]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" refString="Boero, F. &amp; Fresi, E. (1986) Zonation and evolution of a Rocky bottom hydroid community. Marine Ecology, 7 (2), 123 - 150. http: // dx. doi. org / 10.1111 / j. 1439 - 0485.1986. tb 00152. x" type="journal article" year="1986">
