<number box="[487,548,1500,1524]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" value="2002.0">2002</number>
</bibRefCitation>
); from January to December (De Vito 
<number box="[977,1037,1499,1524]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" value="2006.0">2006</number>
