<subSubSection pageId="102" pageNumber="103" type="distribution">
<paragraph blockId="102.[151,1436,1319,2028]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,352,1607,1632]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Distribution.</emphasis>
Although this species has sometimes been thought to be circumtropical, according to 
<bibRefCitation author="Schuchert" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" refString="Schuchert, P. (1997) Review of the family Halopterididae (Hydrozoa, Cnidaria). Zoologische Verhandelingen Leiden, 309, 1 - 162." type="journal article" year="1997">
Schuchert (
<number box="[159,219,1644,1668]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" value="1997.0">1997</number>
)
</bibRefCitation>
, it is actually known only from the Mediterranean and from 
<collectingCountry box="[949,1021,1643,1668]" name="Brazil" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Brazil</collectingCountry>
. It has recently been reported from Florida (
<collectingCountry box="[253,312,1679,1703]" name="United States of America" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">USA</collectingCountry>
) (
<bibRefCitation author="Medel" box="[341,721,1679,1704]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" refString="Medel, M. D. &amp; Lopez-Gonzalez, P. J. (1996) Updated catalogue of the Hydrozoans from the Iberian Peninsula and Balearic Islands with remarks on zoogeography and affinities. Scientia Marina, 60 (1), 183 - 209." type="journal article" year="1996">
Medel &amp; López-González 
<number box="[662,721,1679,1704]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" value="1996.0">1996</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Schuchert" box="[739,924,1679,1704]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" refString="Schuchert, P. (1997) Review of the family Halopterididae (Hydrozoa, Cnidaria). Zoologische Verhandelingen Leiden, 309, 1 - 162." type="journal article" year="1997">
Schuchert 
<number box="[865,924,1679,1703]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" value="1997.0">1997</number>
</bibRefCitation>
; 
<bibRefCitation author="Pena" box="[942,1431,1679,1703]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" refString="Pena Cantero, A. L. &amp; Garcia Carrascosa, A. M. (2002) The benthic hydroid fauna of the Chafarinas Islands (Alboran Sea, western Mediterranean). Zoologische Verhandelingen Leiden, 337, 1 - 180." type="journal article" year="2002">
