<paragraph blockId="102.[151,1436,1319,2028]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,435,1751,1776]" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">Records in Salento.</emphasis>
Common at Torre dell'Inserraglio (
