<taxonomicName class="Hydrozoa" family="Halopterididae" genus="Halopteris" kingdom="Animalia" order="Leptothecata" pageId="102" pageNumber="103" phylum="Cnidaria" rank="species" species="diaphana">
<emphasis italics="true" pageId="102" pageNumber="103">H. diaphana</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is the cornucopia-shaped female gonotheca.
</paragraph>
